'''Raadhiyaam'''
[[File:Radium226.jpg|thumb|Curiyaha Raadhiyaamta.]]

'''Raadhiyaam''' ([[ingiriis]]: Radium) astaanta ([[Ra]]) waa [[curiye]] kimiko oo tirada [[atom]]kiisu tahay sideetan-iyo-sideed (88).
Curiyaha Raadhiyaam waa [[bir]] ka tirsan [[Birta Alkalineta Dhulka]] ee [[guruubka 2]]aad ee [[Diwaanka Curiye]]. 

Raadhiyaamta saafiga ah waxay leedahay [[midab]] cad, laakiin waxay inta badan la [[falgal]]shaa [[Ogsajiin]] taas oo u yeesha midab madoow ah. 
Dhamaan isotopeyada Raadhiyaam waa radioactive leh cimri dhan [[sanad|1610 sano]]. Isotopeka kali ah ee leh elektaroono dagan waa raadhiyaam-226. 

Curiyaha Raadhiyaam waxaa helay labo [[saynis]]yahan Marie Curie iyo Pierre Curie [[sanad|sanadkii 1898]]. 


